[src:reproducible-builds/compiler] GNAT Pro includes the GNU GCC based GNAT with a tool suite to provide an integrated development environment.
[src:reproducible-builds/compiler] High-level languages continued to drive compiler research and development.
[src:reproducible-builds/compiler] Focus areas included optimization and automatic code generation.
